snippet.title: Gunslinger: the first old west duel simulator Indiegogo
snippet.description:
Take your mobile, get ready and Snap! Support us on Indiegogo. You can help us speed up this project and make our vision of Gunslinger a reality. 
Check out the campaign at:
https://igg.me/at/gunslinger
